===== Installation =====
See http://www.haskell.org/haskellwiki/Cabal/How_to_install_a_Cabal_package
===== Usage =====
See rmv-query --help for details.
Example: rmv-query --from Frankfurt --to Darmstadt,Luisenplatz --when 12:00

===== Configuration =====
Each of the command-line flags can be set as a default in the configuration
file(~/.rmv-query). Each line must contain exactly one flag. E.g.:
--from Luisenplatz
--when 8:00

Note: This is experimental software and probably has several bugs.
